title: Brittany Lauryn Cuckold
description: Brittany, similar to whatever other lady, likes to be complimented on her looks. When her significant other Kade started neglecting to do as such with the best possible excitement, she chose to have her hairdresser take a stab at something new: he waxed her beautiful beaver then brought her home for a frolic over the front room while Kade tries to get the bits of his all of a sudden grieved marriage. Perhaps there's promise for Kade yet
